1. DHT11 (Temp & Humidity Sensor)

VCC → 5V of Arduino
GND → GND of Arduino
DATA → D4 of Arduino

2. PIR Motion Sensor

VCC → 5V of Arduino
GND → GND of Arduino
OUT → D3 of Arduino

3. Analog Light Sensor (LDR module / AO pin)

VCC → 5V of Arduino
GND → GND of Arduino
AO → A0 of Arduino

4. Push Button (Dump Logs Trigger)

One side → D2 of Arduino
Other side → GND of Arduino
(Internal pull-up is used in code, no resistor needed)

5. SD Card Module (SPI)

VCC → 5V of Arduino (⚠ check your module, some need 3.3V)
GND → GND of Arduino
CS → D10 of Arduino
MOSI → D11 of Arduino
MISO → D12 of Arduino
SCK → D13 of Arduino